Summary: This section describes the binary serialization format for AABB.

AABB binary serialization format:
*   X coordinate (Float): at offset 4, length 4.
*   Y coordinate (Float): at offset 8, length 4.
*   Z coordinate (Float): at offset 12, length 4.
*   X size (Float): at offset 16, length 4.
*   Y size (Float): at offset 20, length 4.
*   Z size (Float): at offset 24, length 4.
