Document: binary_serialization_api
Path: godot/tutorials/io/binary_serialization_api.rst
Summary: This chunk describes the format for names and sub-names in the binary serialization API.

For new format:
*   Offset 4, Length 4 (Integer): Sub-name count.
*   Offset 8, Length 4 (Integer): Flags (absolute: val&1 != 0).

For each Name and Sub-Name:
*   Offset X+0, Length 4 (Integer): String length.
*   Offset X+4, Length X (Bytes): UTF-8 encoded string.

Every name string is padded to 4 bytes.
---CHUNK---
