Path: godot/tutorials/io/binary_serialization_api.rst
Summary: This chunk describes the binary serialization format for PackedByteArray.

PackedByteArray
- Offset 4, Length 4: Integer representing the array length in bytes.
- Offset 8 to 8+length, Length 1: Byte (0-255).
The array data is padded to 4 bytes.
---CHUNK---
